{"tid":2436612,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"人權大使連尼住支持區","createTime":"2021-03-07T09:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T11:59:58.000Z","uid":344307,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2f8f8c55d20915c7ca437cc3f4e624d4aa315184","tid":2436612,"uid":344307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"咱們連尼住真的是做得好 就算啲五毛滲透哂係連登入面<br />\n<br />\n連尼住老鐵同啲黃絲講我唔想做極權就唔洗做野 打發下佢地就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有越多五毛仲好 最好全中國五毛都入哂嚟連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣就可以賺多啲GOOGLE AD既錢 得閒仲可以賣下公仔<br />\n<br />\n搵多啲外快買下股票 幾撚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面開放支持人權大使連尼住既fans留言 連尼住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fYEcQ6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfYEcQ6K.png&h=ccdfff8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cxvodj5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxvodj5.png&h=213b75c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想買公仔支持連尼住請到TG@lihkgpigfigure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e7770c051cf66a801282054b3788bff000706c","tid":2436612,"uid":344307,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:24:04.000Z","msg":"關閉中天代表政府一言堂？「言論自由」不代表所有內容都應該被允許<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/142407\" data-sr-url=\"